<b>charm is good if know how to use it - </b>11/6/01 6:37:01 AM<br>~ <b>Asurancetturix</b><blockquote>charm song can be great to solo if know how to use it. first of all every bard should have cha over 150(u can get it with 3 or 4 items-kobold jester crown 30, sea spine horse bracelet 10(not sure), mask of deception 13). the number of resists now will be almost none and u probably charm better with 150 cha without flute than less 150 cha with flute. i usually just charm singing and hold in my arms a lute to heal. The tactic is easy, charm a mob and make it follow u. then go near another mob and let it hit u. pet will deffend u and so let em fight and stay enough far away so when charm off u have enough time to recharm. the best place to do this is CS at high 40s low 50s and behind dl ridge from 40. Mana always ends and then i just start doing some chant kitting to recover it.<br>mm sorry if this is too long ;)<br>Asurancetturix bard 55 of sol ro</blockquote></td></tr><tr bgcolor="#eeeeee"><td>
